---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for High in the Sky"
>
  <div class="policy-page">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    
    <section>
      <h2>Introduction</h2>
      <p>
        High in the Sky ("we", "our", or "us") operates the website. This page
        informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use, and
        disclosure of personal data when you use our Service and the choices
        you have associated with that data.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Data Collection</h2>
      <p>
        Our website is a static site hosted on GitHub Pages. We do not collect
        personal information directly. However:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>YouTube Data:</strong> We display videos from YouTube using
          the YouTube API. Please review YouTube's privacy policy for how they
          handle your data.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>GitHub Pages:</strong> Hosting is provided by GitHub. Review
          GitHub's privacy policy for hosting-related data practices.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Third-party Analytics:</strong> If implemented, we use
          analytics services to understand usage patterns.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        Our website does not use cookies to collect personal information. Your
        browser may store cookies for site preferences, but we do not set
        tracking cookies.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>External Links</h2>
      <p>
        Our website may contain links to external sites (YouTube, GitHub, etc.).
        This Privacy Policy does not apply to external websites. We encourage
        you to review their privacy policies.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Security</h2>
      <p>
        We use HTTPS encryption to protect your connection to our site. However,
        no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be
        posted on this page with an updated "Last Modified" date.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please open an issue on
        our GitHub repository or contact us via email.
      </p>
    </section>

    <p><strong>Last Modified:</strong> January 2024</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .policy-page {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .policy-page h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: #1f2937;
  }

  .policy-page h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #1f2937;
  }

  .policy-page section {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .policy-page p {
    color: #374151;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .policy-page ul {
    margin: 1rem 0;
    padding-left: 2rem;
  }

  .policy-page li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: #374151;
  }

  strong {
    color: #1f2937;
  }
</style>
